Whether you’re looking for a pistol based on ergonomics, reliability or features, you’re in the right place. It’s available in a variety of calibers to fit a variety of needs. See how it all started and check out the XD® 4” Full Size. Where you point is where you shoot."

Best miniature gun I have found, just don’t need something this small anymore.  Comes with original case, docs, (2) 6 round flush fit mags and (1) 7 extended magazine.  Just installed fresh springs and disassembled/cleaned the mags. I ran Precision One hollow points when carrying, HPR, Remington or 95 gr reloaded ball ammo for practice. Gun was not reliable with the solid Leigh machined projectiles, (the cross shaped nose would not feed consistently) and did not chamber Fiocchi ammunition due to the case crimp they use on their rounds.  Price is firm, not interested in any trades. Need to see a valid AZ driver’s license or CCW and can provide a bill of sale. Located in Phoenix and can meet most days in the NW valley after 4pm near 101st Ave & Happy Valley Rd or during the day at my work near 33rd St and Broadway.
